sentences: Richie worked at Long's Bar (Tower's Rotana Hotel) in Dubai in 2008 as the resident DJ
Between Fall 2008 and Spring 2009 Richie worked as the Resident DJ at Club Maxxim in Bahrain.
Richie currently works as the resident DJ at Barasti Beach Club in Dubai.
